This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques and deep neural networks for text classification, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with legal case documents, which may involve issues related to security and cryptography (cs.CR).
